    "description": "Feedforce Group Inc. engages in data feed, digital advertising, social media marketing, and other businesses in Japan. It operates through three segments: Professional Services Business; SaaS Business; and DX Business. The company offers dfplus.io, a data feed management tool; Revire, a support service for building corporate websites and systems; and DF PLUS, a data feed outsourcing service. It also provides Anagrams, a marketing support service; Shippinno, an automates shipping-related tasks for e-commerce businesses; Social PLUS, a social login and LINE message delivery service; EC Booster, an automated advertising distribution tool for EC products; and Omni Hub, a service that centralizes member information between the multi-channel commerce platform Shopify and the cloud POS service Smaregi. The company was formerly known as Feedforce Inc. Feedforce Group Inc. was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
